Name: Borsch
Dish description: This Very Special Spirit Is Truly Unique And You Won’t Find Anything Like It Elsewhere In Australia. It Is Not A Vodka Or A Brandy, As It Is Not Distilled From Grains, Potatoes Or Fruit. It Is Actually Distilled From Honey (About Three Litres Per Bottle.) It Then Spends At Least Three Years In Oak Barrels To Produce A Spirit With Incredible Length And Balance. We Are Rather Chuffed To Have It On The Shelf.

Name: Borsch
